<html>

<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="TeacherEvaluateProject.css">
</head>

<script>
    // Sadece sayıya izin veren event listener
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
        const numberInput = document.getElementById("numberInput");

        numberInput.addEventListener("input", (event) => {
            const input = event.target.value;
            // Sadece rakamları tut, diğerlerini temizle
            event.target.value = input.replace(/[^0-9]/g, "");
        });
    });
</script>

<body>

    <div class="all-boxes">

        <div class="intro">
            <h2> Evalute Project </h2>
            <p>Create graduate project for graduation. This is a descriptive text block to navigate the student while he/she creating their team by adding team members, 
             writing the project name and selecting the advisor for project. </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="box-1">
            <h4>AI Supported Human Resources System for IT Companies AI Supported Human Resources System for IT Companies </h4>
            <section class="teamInfo">
                <table class="tableOfTeamInfo">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>
                               <p>Team</p>
                            </th>
                            <th>
                                <p>Status</p>
                            </th>
                            <th>
                                <p>Evaluating Teacher</p>
                            </th>
                            <th>
                                <p>Team Members</p>
                            </th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody id="teamTableBody">
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <p> team name@@Model.Team.TeamName</p>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <p> status @@Model.Team.TeamStatus</p>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <p>advisor @@Model.Team.AdvisorId</p>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <p>team member1</p>
                                @*@foreach (var member in Model.Team.TeamMemberIds)
                                {
                                    <p>@member</p>
                                }*@
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </section>
        </div>
        
        <div class="container">

            <label>
                <input type="radio" name="...">
                Commitment to Impartial Evaluation
            </label>
    
            <div class="section">
                <h3>Part I - Evaluation Project Graduation Form</h3>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>
                        <input type="checkbox" class="checkbox">
                        Technical Merits (%15)
                    </label>
                    <div class="number-only-textarea">
                        <textarea id="numberInput"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <textarea placeholder="Write your thoughts..."></textarea>
                </div>
            </div>
    
            <div class="section">
                <h3>Part II - Graduation Project Checklist</h3>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>
                        <input type="checkbox" class="checkbox">
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vivamus eget porta sapien. Nulla pulvinar tellus justo, a accumsan nunc vehicula a. Cras nec orci nunc. Aenean pellentesque vel nisi ut tempor. Vivamus commodo leo ac porta aliquet. Fusce eu suscipit odio, feugiat pellentesque nulla. Maecenas tellus metus, pellentesque non felis.
                    </label>
                    <textarea placeholder="Write your thoughts..."></textarea>
                </div>
            </div>
    
            <div class="confirmation">
                <label>
                    <input type="radio" name="confirmation">
                    I confirm my evaluation results.
                </label>
            </div>
    
            <button class="evaluate-button">Evaluate</button>
        </div>
    </div>      
</body>
</html>